WEBVTT

00:02.972 --> 00:07.031
In the past, we looked to the West and the East to find inspiration and prosperity.

00:08.957 --> 00:10.951
But now, I look back home to Africa,...

00:12.984 --> 00:16.127
...a vibrant continent full of passionate people.

00:17.971 --> 00:20.353
We thrive and grow energy.

00:22.150 --> 00:24.327
And now, we have something much more powerful:...

00:24.894 --> 00:26.986
...ambition and belief.

00:33.747 --> 00:37.623
When I look at Africa, I see wonderful possibilities for everyone.

00:48.333 --> 00:49.405
Africa is the future.

00:56.263 --> 00:58.569
Discover Africa with us.

